Lista de los filtros
====================
Básicos:
- HOL
- all
- only red
- red and yellow
- only yellow
- blue
- accepted
- reserved

- HOS:
- all
- accepted
- HOS that contain reserved


The advanced search allows the user to find journals and holdings that
comply with a broad range of criteria that can be concatenated and each one
used as a positive or negative filter:

General criteria:
HOL with <field> <compared to> <value>

example: f245a like "biology"


Explanation:
<field>: fields that are used. within zs
<compared to>: equal | not equal | greater than | smaller than | like |
not like | nn% similar to | starts with | ends with
<value>: string | number | regex


Special criteria:
TA:
- continued journal: f008y = '9999' or f866a ~ '->?$'
- ceased journal: f008y <> '9999' or f866a !~ '->?$'
- journal that exists online: online = 'y'
- journal that exists also online: online = 'y' AND f866a
- journal that has been published xy times per year: f310_e ~ ''

HOL:
- HOL that has been marked incomplete by the MAGUSER: incomplete = 'y'
- HOL that has notion of beeing incomplete in f866a: icpl = 'y'
- HOL that has no notion to beeing incomplete in f866a: icpl = 'y'
- HOL that has no notion of incompleteness: icpl = 'n'
- HOL that the MAGUSER marked degraded: sane = 'n'
- HOL that MAGUSER has marked in good estate: sane = 'y'
- HOL that has <more|less|equal> than nn volumes: sum(years)
- HOL which content of field f866a has not been recognized: recognized='n'
created using: hop_result.type !~ '^MDL '
- HOL that has been annotated: update > xxx? AND user = 'USER|*'
- HOL field f866a that has been changed: update > xxx? AND user='USER|*'
- HOL that has been reserved: level = 'reserved'

HOS:
- HOS that has <less|equal|more> than nn HOL
- HOS that has been marked correct: xxx? = 'y'
- HOS that has been changed: been: update > xxx? AND user='USER|*'





